You are helping build a personal portfolio website for a Media Design student.

## Project
- Static HTML/CSS/JS site, no frameworks
- Files: index.html, bio.html, portfolio.html, lavoro-1/2/3.html, contatti.html
- CSS in /css/style.css, images in /img/, scripts in /js/main.js

## Design system
- Primary: #FF4D0A
- Accent: #000000
- Background: #ffffff
- Text: #FF4D0A
- Title font: Public Sans
- Body font: Inter

## Rules
- Always use CSS custom properties (--color-primary, etc.), never hardcode colors
- Use semantic HTML5 tags (header, main, section, article, nav, footer)
- All images must have descriptive alt attributes
- CSS organized in sections: reset, variables, typography, layout, components, pages
- Mobile-first: breakpoints at 768px (tablet) and 1024px (desktop)
